comments: Duren (DET) legally contests Porzingis' (BOS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Duren (DET) establishes himself in Holiday's (BOS) path and marginal body contact occurs as he defends over the pick.
Bogdanovic (DET) and White (BOS) briefly engage and disengage during the screen.
Porzingis (BOS) extends his right arm outward and initiates illegal contact with Ivey's (DET) shoulder during his driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Tatum (BOS) loses control of the ball out of bounds.
After the release of the jump shot, Ivey (DET) turns into Porzingis (BOS) and the contact is marginal.
Cunningham (DET) is retracting his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs with Porzingis (BOS) during his post shot attempt.
As the ball becomes loose, Holiday (BOS) and Duren (DET) make incidental foot contact with the ball during the pursuit of the rebound.

After Holiday (BOS) secures the loose ball, Bogdanovic (DET) reaches forwards and makes slight contact with his head.   Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Ivey (DET) reaches in and initiates contact with Porzingis' (BOS) forearm that affects his SQBR after securing the pass.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending violation by Cunningham (DET) stands, as there is no clear and conclusive evidence to overturn the call on the floor.
Holiday (BOS) legally contests Cunningham's (DET) jump shot, making incidental "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
White (BOS) rests a hand on Bogdanovic's (DET) front, but the marginal contact does not affect his put-back shot attempt.
White (BOS) initiates contact with Duren's (DET) right arm, affecting his shot attempt near the rim.
Horford (BOS) clamps and holds Livers' (DET) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Duren (DET) places his forearm against Horford's (BOS) side and Horford briefly places an arm around Duren as the two players engage during the rebound.
Bogdanovic (DET) commits a take foul on Porzingis (BOS).
Cunningham (DET) intentionally kicks the ball.
Burks (DET) commits a take foul on Holiday (BOS).
Bogdanovic (DET) commits a take foul on White (BOS).
